com.capricorn.listener

Class StartPractice

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.capricorn.listener.StartPractice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class StartPractice
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    This is the enter to the practice game. If the client want to be familiar with the game before the true competition. Here is a good place for the player to have fun and practice. This function do not need to connect to sever, so no request and response will generate or receive.
    Author:
    Chen Li, Dongsheng Wang, Yu Li, Tianyu Wu, Bowen Sun
